lackpink-rose-inks-deal-atlantic-records-upcoming-solo-releases-3797554">这位韩国流行歌星与大西洋唱片公司签署协议</a>后不久，就宣布了“rosie”的消息。当时，Rosé 还推出了她的新“finsta”帐户<a href="https://www.instagram.com/vampirehollie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@vampirehollie</a> ，她和她的团队将在其中分享她即将推出的独奏音乐的最新动态。值得注意的是，该账户名与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-tease-new-song-vampirehollie-instagram-3586437">她二月份向粉丝取笑的一首即将发行的歌曲</a>同名。</p><p>六月，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行</a>歌星透露，她已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-new-music-not-too-distant-future-3767087">与 The Black Label 签约</a>进行个人活动。六个月前，BLACKPINK 的四名成员决定在 2023 年底不再与 YG Entertainment 续签个人合同。</p><p>这位歌手即将发行的专辑将是她自 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194">首张单曲专辑《R》</a>以来的首张个人音乐，其中包括歌曲《On The Ground》和《Gone》。她还在 BLACKPINK 2022 年录音室专辑《Born Pink》中演唱了独奏曲目《Hard To Love》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-studio-album-rosie-3798825">BLACKPINK 的 Rosé 宣布首张个人录音室专辑“rosie”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
杰克·安东诺夫希望在 LGBTQ+ 青少年收容所建立公共录音室https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-wants-to-build-public-recording-studios-in-lgbtq-youth-shelters-3798819?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jack-antonoff-想要在 LGBTQ 青少年庇护所建造公共录音工作室Surej SinghWed, 02 Oct 2024 03:34:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3798819 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们的计划是建造这些空间，支付维护和工程费用，并让中心为人们提供使用它们的时间段”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-antonoff-wants-to-build-public-recording-studios-in-lgbtq-youth-shelters-3798819">杰克·安东诺夫希望在 LGBTQ+ 青少年收容所建立公共录音室的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jack-antonoff@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff)</a>透露了他计划在美国各地的几个 LGBTQ+ 青少年庇护所建造公共录音室 - 看看他在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/jack-antonoff-bleachers-grammy-3619474">杰克·安东诺夫：“我一直觉得自己真的被误解了——这就像我内心有一种强烈的、沉重的感觉”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（10 月 1 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a>主唱兼热门制作人在社交媒体上分享了一份声明，概述了他在“我人生下一个篇章的大部分时间”中建立多个此类工作室的意图。</p><p>安东诺夫在帖子中写道，他很高兴能够在任何地方进行制作——从家庭录音室到酒店房间，甚至在路上的飞机上——但他的生活“在录音室里改变了”，“是时候分享这一点了”与那些可能不会发现自己在那里但需要在那里的人一起。” </p><figure id="attachment_3612902" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3612902" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3612902" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff.jpg" alt="看台" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/bleachers_jack_antonoff-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3612902" class="wp-caption-text"> Bleachers 乐队的 Jack Antonoff 于 2024 年 3 月 19 日在英国伦敦肯特镇 O2 论坛表演。 （洛恩·汤姆森/雷德芬斯摄）</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“我计划在人生的下一个篇章中花费大部分时间，将这些空间带给那些无法进入的人们。公共工作室可供那些价格合理的人使用。这需要时间和大量资源，但我们有一个计划，首先通过盟友联盟在 LGBTQ+ 青少年庇护所建立工作室。从那里开始，我们的计划是建造这些空间，支付维护和工程费用，并让中心为人们提供使用它们的时间段。一旦实现，我们就可以从那里开始扩展到城市。”</p><p>至于宣布计划的原因，安东诺夫希望它能提高人们对这一事业的认识，并激励“任何相信这一点并拥有可以提供帮助的资源的人”，然后再添加一条伸出援手的热线。</p><p>安东诺夫在结束他的帖子时谈到了“我喜欢的所有商业工作室”：“这个概念严格适用于那些无力承担在这些空间中的工作室时间的人，所以我相信这对我们的空间也有帮助”。</p><p>请阅读下面安东诺夫的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAls-nXxPr7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.8